#Text=Dress Appropriately
#Text=Sometimes you need to dress nicely .
#Text=Sometimes you do n't .
#Text=But all the time , you need to dress in a way that compliments you and others .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Organize your closet .
#Text=Fold your clothes neatly , hang up your dresses and jeans , and sort shirts and shorts into drawers or baskets .
#Text=Find out where you are going .
#Text=You do n't want to go to the grocery store in your favorite Sunday clothes , and you probably would n't like to go to a fancy restaurant in your PJ 's .
#Text=Pick out an outfit .
#Text=First , choose a shirt or blouse .
#Text=Then find a skirt or pants to go with it .
#Text=Picking the top first helps you picture the entire outfit better .
#Text=Accessorize !
#Text=Jewelry is very important to the entire appearance , since it ties the whole outfit together and adds a focal point .
#Text=Also , you should make sure that if you are going to carry a handbag or purse , be sure that it does not contrast too much .
#Text=With shoes , be sure that they are comfortable and will not attract too much attention .
#Text=Apply makeup right before leaving .
#Text=Do n't put on too much- you should n't want to appear fake .
#Text=You do n't want it to look like you have makeup on .
#Text=Less is best sometimes especially when you are older and start to have some wrinkles .
#Text=Smile and be kind .
#Text=A person is only as good as her personality , and you do n't want people to think that you are sour or unkind .
#Text=Check some style websites and see what the different age groups are wearing .
#Text=Copy it or as close as you can .
#Text=Like what you wear and be comfortable in your cloths .
#Text=Tips
#Text=Dress yourself nicely wherever you go .
#Text=People notice if you do n't take care of yourself , and when you do , chances are that others will be more open to meeting and talking to you .
#Text=Be confident ! A sparkling smile is an important part of any outfit .
#Text=Look people in the eye when meeting them or speaking to them , and always offer your hand to shake before and after introducing yourself .
#Text=Always be friendly to people .
#Text=Do n't insult them when talking to them .
#Text=Also , keep eye contact when they are speaking to you .
#Text=It shows that you are paying attention and it says , " I respect your values and opinions .
